OL,3,CLabour MP admits defeat in Birmingham
OL,4,CCity Council elections
OL,6,FA Birmingham MP has admitted defeat
OL,7,Ffor Labour in the city council
OL,8,Felections.
OL,10,FSpeaking to ITV News Central Laurence
OL,11,FTurner, the MP for Birmingham
OL,12,FNorthfield said, "It does look like
OL,13,Fwe're heading for a period in
OL,14,Fopposition."
OL,16,FReform UK's deputy leader Richard Tice
OL,17,Fhas already arrived at the Birmingham
OL,18,FCity Council election count to
OL,19,Fcelebrate his party's gains there.
OL,26,@tD@ROUvD@LO]
