OL,3,CLabour MP admits defeat in Birmingham
OL,4,CCity Council elections
OL,6,FFinal results aren't expected until
OL,7,Fafter 6pm but Tice has said the party
OL,8,F"absolutely smashed it" in other areas
OL,9,Fof the West Midlands, including
OL,10,FNewcastle-under-Lyme and Tamworth.
OL,12,FA Labour source has told ITV Central
OL,13,Fpolitical reporter Lewis Warner that
OL,14,Fthey're expecting to win fewer than 20
OL,15,Fseats in Birmingham.JThe party won 65
OL,16,Fat the last election.
OL,18,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,19,Four political experts are across all
OL,20,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,21,Fto the latest episode below...
